Package: roller
Type: Package
Title: Performs a "roll" on a multi sided device and displays accompanying 
    statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Horton Papa
Maintainer: Horton Papa <horton.papa@berkeley.edu>
Description: This package allows the user to create an object, that can have 
    multiple sides, and perform a "roll" operation on the object. The roll
    essentially creates a vector of outcomes for each roll.
